title: SwifTEA: Taylor Breaks Her Silence For "Carolina"
description:
Taylor Swift has been silent for a while, but she's coming out of hiding to talk about "Carolina"! What other theories has this led to? We break it down and discuss the possibilities!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
